metadata.name: To The Moon Lucky Rabbit
metadata.description:
Celebrating the Year of the Rabbit with a collection of lucky rabbits that will add good vibes to your life.

In the Chinese zodiac, the Rabbit is associated with traits such as kindness, compassion, and sensitivity. It is also thought to symbolize good luck and prosperity. Additionally, the rabbit is said to be a peaceful, gentle, and sensitive sign that is also quite shy. They are also known for being quite artistic.

The Year of the Rabbit in the Chinese zodiac is associated with calmness, diplomacy, and good luck. The Rabbit is also associated with good fortune and prosperity, making it a favorable year for business and financial matters. It is also said to be an ideal time for families to grow and for people to focus on their home and personal life.
